    "In Table 5, after stepwise regression screening, there is a statistically significant correlation between an algorithm and the characteristics of a dataset, which is represented by \"√\".",
    "With \"recommend or not\" as the target variable and 26 data sets quantization characteristics as attribute variables, a decision tree model is constructed using C4.5 algorithm.",
    "The applicability judgment decision tree of 8 algorithms obtained on continuous variable datasets are built.",
    "According to these decision trees, the applicability of 8 algorithms on continuous variable datasets can be judged and predicted.",
    "Through the validation on the training set and test set of the algorithm applicability metadata, both the decision tree judgment model and the stepwise regression judgment model reached the accuracy of more than 75%."
